===Noun===
{{en-noun|~|radars}}

# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} A method of [[detecting]] [[distant]] [[object]]s and [[determining]] their [[position]], [[velocity]], or other characteristics by [[analysis]] of sent [[radio]] [[wave]]s (usually microwaves) [[reflect]]ed from their [[surface]]s
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A type of system using such method, differentiated by platform, configuration, frequency, power, and other technical attributes.
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} An installation of such a system or of the transmitting and receiving apparatus.
# {{context|countable|figuratively|lang=en}} A superior ability to detect something.
#: ''His sensitive '''radar''' for hidden alliances keeps him out of trouble.''

